{"tid":386396,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"澳門立會選舉　賭王四太母子檔參選","createTime":"2017-09-03T23:45:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T01:38:41.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c7764a259d86ea5ce0ee2a61337e0ea5c76f7582","tid":386396,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:45:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170903/large/1504454023_71c8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170903%2Flarge%2F1504454023_71c8.jpg&h=0bca98cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（陳善南攝）(蘋果日報)<br />\n<br />\n澳門立法會選舉投票日於9月17號舉行，今年賭王「四太」梁安琪攜同兒子何猷亨參選，今晚一眾「澳門發展新連盟」候選人出席造勢大會，惟天公不作美，大會一開始，天便下起傾盤大雨，臨近大會結束，梁安琪及兒子何猷亨才出現，上台與一眾候選人高唱參選主題曲，梁安琪指成員來自不同界別，是希望將不同聲音帶入議會，平衡各界利益。<br />\n<br />\n澳門上星期受到兩個颱風襲擊，對澳門造成嚴重影摧毀，何太接受訪問指風災確實對澳門帶來創傷，但各界人士齊心救災，令澳門得以盡快恢復，她亦相信澳門人能盡快恢復心情，盡公民盡任支持一個「盡市民責任」的選舉，「當日我都有講過係唔係將呢嗰（選舉）會壓後少少呢，大家嘅心情會好啲呢，咁選管會亦都冇押後，咁唔緊要啦，咁大家就努力去做啦」。<br />\n<br />\n風災後不少人指責澳門議員未盡力救災，何太指該指責是錯誤的，「我相信議會每一位議員都有好，其實大家睇到，只不過議員唔係一定要去影相，唔係一定要去post一啲什麼東西(上網）。」何太指颱風襲澳期間已有立即進行救災，只是沒有拍照公諸於世。何太強調選舉期間不想提及救災工作，「我覺得係選舉期間我哋唔提呢啲野，我哋將呢個風災嘅嘢抹左佢啦，我哋眼向前望。」<br />\n<br />\n問及期望能取得幾席，何太回應指會盡力做好，「當然越多越好啦，相信大家睇到我哋呢個組別，我哋將各界嘅聲音都帶到議會，監督政府嘅施政。」何太指「澳門發展新連盟」成員來自不同界別，是為了平衡各界的利益，「我哋唔係偏激嘅，我哋最緊要起到中間點樣和諧，咁相信呢個係大家有目共睹嘅。」<br />\n<br />\n「澳門發展新連盟」成員中有多個年輕人，何太於訪問中提到自己年紀大，希望將年輕一輩帶入議會，「如果有機會市民將我哋帶入議會，打後來我哋會更加培育我哋年青一代。」問及今次連同兒子何猷亨一同參選，是否培養兒子成為接班人，何太回應指，「我個仔好有心去做社會工作，咁唔係一個接唔接班，其實係用心、用力去為社會。」<br />\n<br />\n問及何猷亨對選舉有無信心，何回應指「咁所有野不嬲做人唔做人啦，做任何事都要有信心，如果你冇信心嘅話你已經輸咗，咁當然係有信心。」何猷亨表示假若當選，會較關注年輕人的議題，包括青年宿舍、年輕人置業等問題。<br />\n<br />\n「澳門發展新連盟」第2號候選人關偉霖認為經歷風災後，相信更多選民會投票，因選民會對不同候選人於風災中的賑災工作進行判斷，從而作出決定，「邊個幫到佢嘅，佢就會一定會係加重一啲同情分，我估呢個一定會刺激個投票意欲。」關偉霖稱選民會將票投給「全心為市民」的候選人。問及對選舉有無信心，關偉霖指過往的社會工作若得到選民認同，選民自然會支持，「如果個市民認同你，你唔係同佢同一個鼻孔呼吸嘅，我諗你點樣用呢兩個星期嘅宣傳，都唔會改變到佢哋嘅投票意欲。」<br />\n<br />\n有言論指關偉霖與江湖人士熟絡，關偉霖指：「從來冇啲咁嘅時，如果係澳門認識我嘅人，我打開個肚皮仲白過個白豬仔，全部嗰啲都係網上嘅欲加之罪，呢啲我好難去回應，咁自己清者自清。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57165743&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57165743%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=e011e099\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D57165743%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170904&h=68e47057\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=57165743&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170904</a>"},{"pid":"7bd769733a3993327c2fd64c40a03e45a3042a77","tid":386396,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:50:50.000Z","msg":"女特首<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d012ed2fbbb5e48bc7b84645a38de18f9ca8447b","tid":386396,"uid":63450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T23:58:18.000Z","msg":"官 商 x x<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecee449a58dbdcaad737e5f437ffb20ecd1a67b8","tid":386396,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T00:08:02.000Z","msg":"有做過既點會唔提自己係風後既工作<br />\n叫人抹左佢, 唔好提<br />\n係咪話自己無出過力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e20e7ce69fbd4731b0f940ae5d6a42708894414e","tid":386396,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:22:44.000Z","msg":"講得平衡各界利益即係無立場啦扮中立啦"},{"pid":"f5fba6dfb1a47c6767abf8af9552165fad19c98e","tid":386396,"uid":13503,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:24:54.000Z","msg":"澳門立法會洗撚投票直接由賭場委任仲實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfcdfc2a26f10904095721d013c6946438128c0","tid":386396,"uid":9230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講得平衡各界利益即係無立場啦扮中立啦</blockquote><br />\n各界係講緊政界、商界同賭場界呀"},{"pid":"aeaf36cdb79a900047b7513459610dd0ed8e751c","tid":386396,"uid":67302,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T01:58:57.000Z","msg":"唔投佢天日見到全家比人棄屍街頭"},{"pid":"4f34f9e2422e351b519ff3b71ead1926e039d5f8","tid":386396,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:07:46.000Z","msg":"澳門立法會有用架咩"},{"pid":"1679112f6c5a176b260ee73f03d2827db408bec0","tid":386396,"uid":22694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:17:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔投佢天日見到全家比人棄屍街頭</blockquote><br />\n墨西哥咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c03e6657802e552d0ad940f269f90b68378dfa71","tid":386396,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"官商勾結 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"22e1a347694a913cf23db2e91d5db3d783be148d","tid":386396,"uid":37522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T02:21:04.000Z","msg":"澳門唔駛選啦<br />\n<br />\n整個功能界別59席賭業，1席杏仁餅業就得啦"},{"pid":"6c5a67e6523ccea9e6ff4996332e8bbd31d80f12","tid":386396,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T05:44:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳門唔駛選啦<br />\n<br />\n整個功能界別59席賭業，1席杏仁餅業就得啦</blockquote><br />\n桑拿業呢"},{"pid":"8a6d86365bce55dba4a271e8b6ed95d6032bf8f2","tid":386396,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-04T23:59:50.000Z","msg":"<strong>四太爭連任　與兒子何猷亨同一名單</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/21369128_717196105144188_5112972284600176381_n_DA2MT_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F21369128_717196105144188_5112972284600176381_n_DA2MT_1200x0.jpg&h=c4332bd7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n四太梁安琪（左一）與兒子何猷亨（右一）一同落區宣傳。來源：梁安琪社交網站<br />\n<br />\n澳門立法會選舉將於本月17日舉行，宣傳期亦已於9月2日開始，各個組別開始拉票活動，其中賭王何鴻燊四太、現任澳門立法會議員梁安琪更與兒子何猷亨一同參選。<br />\n<br />\n四太梁安琪自2005年起擔任澳門立法會議員，今屆排在14號「澳門發展新連盟」名單第一位，爭取四度連任。其名單第二位為連續兩次高票落選的老拍檔關偉霖，四房長子、澳博助理營運總裁何猷亨排在名單第三位，首次與母親梁安琪拍一同參選。<br />\n<br />\n「澳門發展新連盟」於上周六（2日）下午即舉行政綱發布會，梁安琪首先介紹政綱框架，包括發展第一、宜居為要、青年優先、教育為基等八大要點，其拍擋關偉霖指，「發展第一」即提倡多元博彩，透過經濟發展帶來新空間，創造更多新職位。<br />\n<br />\n對於天鴿風災襲澳後，不少人指責當地議員未盡力救災，梁安琪接受《蘋果日報》訪問時認為指責是錯誤的，指自己亦有立即救災，只是沒有拍照。梁安琪又強調，選舉期間不想提及救災工作，「我覺得係選舉期間我哋唔提呢啲野，我哋將呢個風災嘅嘢抹左佢啦，我哋眼向前望。」<br />\n<br />\n早前澳門受「天鴿」影響，澳門停水停電。何猷亨在社交網站貼文，翌日即由港回澳，在母親辦事處派水。<br />\n<br />\n今年五月，何猷亨亦升任澳博助理營運總裁，更多次與母同場出席公開活動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/21199627_305353013267503_6714537343705921692_o_FUD6v_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F21199627_305353013267503_6714537343705921692_o_FUD6v_1200x0.jpg&h=4fba6865&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：何猷亨社交網站<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%BE%B3%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%AA%E7%88%AD%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB-%E8%88%87%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E4%BD%95%E7%8C%B7%E4%BA%A8%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%2588%25AD%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BD%2595%25E7%258C%25B7%25E4%25BA%25A8%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%2F&d=eSihygRt4ZE%2FMn2LPEVkfgtTNu1qqkxUxYmVHECffP4%3D&h=552654f2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%2F%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E8%2588%2589-%25E5%259B%259B%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E7%2588%25AD%25E9%2580%25A3%25E4%25BB%25BB-%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%2585%2592%25E5%25AD%2590%25E4%25BD%2595%25E7%258C%25B7%25E4%25BA%25A8%25E5%2590%258C%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%2590%258D%25E5%2596%25AE%2F&h=905d717c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80/%E6%BE%B3%E7%AB%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%81%B8%E8%88%89-%E5%9B%9B%E5%A4%AA%E7%88%AD%E9%80%A3%E4%BB%BB-%E8%88%87%E5%85%92%E5%AD%90%E4%BD%95%E7%8C%B7%E4%BA%A8%E5%90%8C%E4%B8%80%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE/</a>"},{"pid":"187470a42bffced0b2e0ed23d75d0f8da295df69","tid":386396,"uid":84275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:08:33.000Z","msg":"肯出黎做下大龍鳳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你班澳門人仲想點<br />\n人地委任嫁嘛"},{"pid":"9f918480d2b27e9fe614d48dc7b08028df332c62","tid":386396,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>澳門唔駛選啦<br />\n<br />\n整個功能界別59席賭業，1席杏仁餅業就得啦</blockquote><br />\n桑拿業呢</blockquote><br />\n博彩界（一）、博彩界（二）......<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bf66fdc1c6c61204d58d9c135714091cc197a286","tid":386396,"uid":61994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T00:56:42.000Z","msg":"佢個仔個樣想點，小學雞俾人迫咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc84d1220888da8cab70b74352ade344203716c8","tid":386396,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:18:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔投佢天日見到全家比人棄屍街頭</blockquote><br />\n今時今日佢有撚能力咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59ca400606849a295d4efa65fc808f6feb72266f","tid":386396,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:28:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢個仔個樣想點，小學雞俾人迫咁款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\